{"tid":2505563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平訪廣西桂林  提出“不惜血戰”堅持下去","createTime":"2021-04-26T16:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T22:21:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fe603749278eb39bdf848822c851a7fca6f80474","tid":2505563,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:27:42.000Z","msg":"中國官媒新華網的微博4月26日帖文介紹，習近平在廣西桂林全州縣才灣鎮紅軍湘江戰役紀念園參觀時表示，困難再大，&ldquo;就想想紅軍長征，想想湘江血戰&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，革命能成功的奧秘是&ldquo;在最困難的時候堅持下去&rdquo;，這樣才能不斷取得&ldquo;奇蹟般的勝利&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n習近平強調，&ldquo;紅軍將士視死如歸、向死而生、一往無前，靠的是理想信念&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/中國/20210426-習近平突訪紅軍紀念園-提-不惜血戰-堅持下去\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20210426-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%AA%81%E8%A8%AA%E7%B4%85%E8%BB%8D%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E5%9C%92-%E6%8F%90-%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%9C%E8%A1%80%E6%88%B0-%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8B%E5%8E%BB&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B660IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=90a5fe74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/cn/中國/20210426-習近平突訪紅軍紀念園-提-不惜血戰-堅持下去</a>"},{"pid":"c8cb23638e528fdbe8b4f80c8cc5d5005ed5c34d","tid":2505563,"uid":89608,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"又唔洗講到咁盡, 人地真係會淆, <br />\n淆左就無謂啦"},{"pid":"fec658e4470c13758bb20f7b07d14fd35c82b1b4","tid":2505563,"uid":257272,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:34:42.000Z","msg":"習近平: 你地負責血戰, 我負責勝利(精神勝利)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a27d27257a953575c555cfa818ca7eec58bd03c","tid":2505563,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"血戰 我諗起一套動畫叫 Blood+"},{"pid":"4b67e700d256f2bb369b803280f2d8b6463ac286","tid":2505563,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"寄語港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im